sequenceDiagram
    participant App as 应用启动
    participant Snap as hooksConfigSnapshot
    participant Settings as settings.json
    participant Session as 会话执行中

    App->>Snap: captureHooksConfigSnapshot()
    Snap->>Settings: 读取当前配置（含策略过滤）
    Settings-->>Snap: HooksSettings（快照）
    Note over Snap: initialHooksConfig = 快照
    Session->>Snap: getHooksConfigFromSnapshot()
    Snap-->>Session: 返回快照（不读磁盘）
    Note over Settings: 用户修改 settings.json
    Session->>Snap: getHooksConfigFromSnapshot()
    Snap-->>Session: 仍返回原快照（隔离）
    App->>Snap: updateHooksConfigSnapshot()
    Snap->>Settings: resetSettingsCache() + 重新读取
    Settings-->>Snap: 新的 HooksSettings
    Note over Snap: initialHooksConfig = 新快照
